{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they used to have what they called the [GERMAN], which is giving a notice just on the walls.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people were told that you-- the Jews have to move out from this streets for three hours a day or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say its-- the start is July 15, but most probably [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] maybe at the end of July, as far as since the movement of the people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But official, I would say it was July 15th when it started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It started to restrictions, and then it became already a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- the-- the Polish population or the white Russian population was out of the places as it moved on further.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then it was only Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I would say before July 15th, until by the end of the month it was all Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't change yet too much, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't-- there wasn't wires yet separately and apart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even so there were already some wires in some places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in November already when the first slaughter of the Jews took place, there was already segregated with wires.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but it wasn't-- as when I was later in the ghettos, you know, with guards and-- it-- it wasn't that nature yet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was still wires.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a main gate that you had to go in and out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But not even '41 year, there was no gates and entry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That is the entry where you enter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was in the later one that it was already had a main gate, and the wires were all around, and guards were already walking around.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't even too much guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were separated already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Around that time when the first slaughter started November 14th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
